content: Just For Today
Honestly it keeps me honest and my date growing.
Its not opening....staying on blue screen..doesn't work. No response from support. Not very happy with this app, as paid for it but doesn't work

I've gotten a lot of mileage out of this app, thank you for your service putting it together. There are a couple of issues, IMO. I don't have Android coding experience, so can't to speak directly to those mechanics. The soft buttons used to page forward & backward through the readings pages. Also, it seems like the cut/paste integration with the system UI is broken. It's been awhile since an update, so maybe some code tweaking could address these. Hope this helps & thanks for reading. ~Scott
Broke, app doesn't work just freezes after I enter my pin
Wont open pass the first screen after entering my pin.

Got this app yesterday and made my first entry. I'm trying to open it now and it just sits there on the beginning "blue" screen after I enter my pin code and I have to force close it to try again. Did this 4x and still can't get in. Please get this fixed and I can change my review after I have some more experience with it

Electronic version of IP#9 "Living The Program" Hello: I really don't understand why there are several negative reviews here. I've been using this app for several years now. When I used to do the "Living The Program" inventory I typed all the questions up on a blank Word document and left it on the desktop of my computer. Now, this app makes it so simple and easy to do a daily inventory or 10th Step! The only thing that is missing is the prayer from the IP; all the rest is there, though.

I cant get it to log in my pin all of a sudden it will not work
App stopped working. Will not open after entering my PIN. I have uninstalled and reinstalled it several times but still same result. Any suggestions?
Great app. Just love it
App is good for tracking the clean start date, but I couldn't get the daily inventory to log my answers and the website is just easier to use.
Would be better if it included a basic text

Decent app. Although most of the app just links to webpages. Just for today is just a web link. I did find the living the program Q&A insightful. I would think being a nonprofit organization this app would be free. Especially since it's quick links to web pages. Keep coming back.
I liked it alot except it gets stuck on the clean date counter
I love the program, but the clean time counter is off by 3 days, so in order to have the correct clean time reflection, I had to put in the wrong clean date.
Great
the just for today reading wont pull up anymore.
Loved it
The app doesn't save my entries anymore and if I email them to myself they save as blank. So I'm unable to see the patterns forming??? Please remedy this. Thanks

Lovely app to have on the phone, close to hand all the time. Is it possible to have the JFT update at midnight in different time zones? Currently when I look at JFT every morning in the UK it is still yesterday's reading.  Many thanks.
It has all the tools I need to start my day.  Awesome  app
I'm o.k. with the app, It has what I need at this point in my recovery.

I love this app because I can quickly pull up the JFT and do a daily inventory. I did just notice today however that the clean time counter is off? I have the correct clean date in there but it says I have 3 days less than I actually do. I even looked at a calendar and did the math... I thought this was very strange. (I've had this app for 6 months and just noticed this error.)
call sponsor doesn't work, and everything else just brings you to different websites. not worthwhile for $3.
Sponsor option not syncing with contact info.
Uninstalled, reinstalled, accepted ability to access contacts, entered sponsor contact. Still doesn't work. Love the rest but this is frustrating. Thanks!
I can't read any of the pamphlets even though I have downloaded multiple pdf readers. Also, the call sponsor part won't load.
Recover or die
No excuse not to use it
Love the app. Daily inventory, all the group readings, links to JFT and meetings, and shortcut to call your sponsor.
Check it.
